{"TopicId":8509,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Switching between ships?","CreatedByName":"Ghost4000","CreatedById":19975,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T22:42:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Ghost4000","CreatedById":19975,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T22:42:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs it possible? How?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"trbinsc","CreatedById":10144,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T22:54:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you are using the 0.14 version you can switch from the tracking station.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryten","CreatedById":348,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T22:54:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022trbinsc\u0022 data-cite=\u0022trbinsc\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you are using the 0.14 version you can switch from the tracking station.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr by using the [ and ] keys.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"trbinsc","CreatedById":10144,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T22:55:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kryten\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Kryten\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr by using the [ and ] keys.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr double-clicking on the map.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ghost4000","CreatedById":19975,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-22T23:55:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI am using whatever version you get when you pay for it....but without the update from the updater because it isn\\\u0027t working for me. \u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"trbinsc","CreatedById":10144,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-23T00:03:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen you start the game, is there a satellite dish there?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ghost4000","CreatedById":19975,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-23T00:35:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Feragorn","CreatedById":7549,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-23T00:43:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThen all of the suggestions will work.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryten","CreatedById":348,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-23T16:38:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou need to make sure to press \\\u0027space centre\\\u0027 rather than \\\u0027end flight\\\u0027 when leaving a ship, or there won\\\u0027t be any ships to switch between.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ghost4000","CreatedById":19975,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-03-23T18:44:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kryten\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Kryten\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou need to make sure to press \\\u0027space centre\\\u0027 rather than \\\u0027end flight\\\u0027 when leaving a ship, or there won\\\u0027t be any ships to switch between.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThank you that helped a lot. \u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}